{"tid":2059486,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：唱「榮光」屬政治宣傳　「孤星淚」視乎情況","createTime":"2020-06-11T03:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T03:42:42.000Z","uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66e54320e0369531fd2ff4b29957e5bc28af39cd","tid":2059486,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信中提及，不應在校園內唱帶有政治訊息的歌曲作政治表態，楊潤雄在一個電台節目被問到是否不容許唱反修例歌曲《願榮光歸香港》時表示，很難逐首歌評論，坊間有很多創意，不斷有新歌或改編歌，這首歌很明顯是政治上宣傳的歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n至於學生在學校音樂比賽唱革命歌曲《孤星淚》又是否容許，楊潤雄說，覺得《孤星淚》可以唱，但要視乎當時環境、目的、宗旨，會否干擾校園，或帶有政治目標鼓勵其他同學，干擾校園影響情緒及學習。他說，不是歌詞字眼問題，而是背後是否推動一些東西。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531415-20200611.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531415-20200611.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRHG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=e2c0fa05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531415-20200611.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=57769673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531415-20200611.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b89f6896eb1841f759e22902aa9658c7dee822ef","tid":2059486,"uid":332804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"最弱智係套歪理，支持佢就應該，反對佢就政治。"},{"pid":"50de23ba081682d332e0dba8d6ab8a2284c59fc3","tid":2059486,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"當大家仲係度內鬥嘅時候，麻煩你睇下流亡台灣嘅手足點講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059034</a>"},{"pid":"096a6d1835d38796f8949b17e072380ff5580faa","tid":2059486,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"唱義勇軍進行曲就唔係"},{"pid":"ba9865a903580a966e24abc3